<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 01:43:36 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a1b924108d93</link><description>&lt;p&gt;现在。我们等待。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt='A modern car wash at night with a glowing red arch and illuminated "CAR WASH" sign above large glass windows revealing interior equipment.' height="6048" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/itsbrian/6a1b924108d93.jpg" width="8064"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://itsbrian.some.pics"&gt;@itsbrian&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 01:43:36 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>烘焙孙女生日蛋糕</title><link>https://some.pics/6a1b7826f3554</link><description>&lt;p&gt;烤我1岁孙女的生日蛋糕。巧克力夹层蛋糕配巧克力糖霜。第一步完成，现在只需等它们冷却。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Three l round nine inch diameter chocolate cakes, sitting on a stovetop, lined up and cooling off." height="2802" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/swrogers/6a1b7826f3554.jpg" width="3178"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://swrogers.some.pics"&gt;@swrogers&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 23:52:10 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>墙面艺术装饰</title><link>https://some.pics/6a1b747db41b5</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在我办公桌后面的墙上加了一些艺术品。还有几件要添上，把空缺的地方填满，但还需要更多的画框。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Added some art to the wall behind my desk. I have a few more pieces to add and fill in the holes, but I need more frames. " height="3658" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/teejay/6a1b747db41b5.jpg" width="4878"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://teejay.some.pics"&gt;@teejay&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 23:36:33 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a1b7313c3030</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我亲爱的伴侣带我去参加了一个烹饪课，作为提前的生日礼物！我们做了带阿根廷香辣酱的侧腹牛排、普普萨饼和红酱。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="My wonderful partner took me to a cooking class as an early birthday present! Flank steak with chimichurri sauce, pupusas, and  salsa roja" height="1506" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/b00ksc0ut/6a1b7313c3030.jpg" width="2000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://b00ksc0ut.some.pics"&gt;@b00ksc0ut&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 23:30:39 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a1b551431294</link><description>&lt;p&gt;蓝花楹&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Purple flowers on a jacaranda tree against a blue sky." height="3021" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/macmanx/6a1b551431294.jpg" width="4028"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://macmanx.some.pics"&gt;@macmanx&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 21:22:32 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>